                  </hi>. I am the officer. I took the prisoner, and have the handkerchief now.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence</hi>, I saw two boys about the prosecutor—one did pick his pocket, I passed between, a lady and gentleman, and he turned and took hold of me.</p>
